": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sasha_Abramsky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sasha Abramsky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sasha_Abramsky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sasha_Abramsky\"}, {\"begin\": 5883, \"end\": 5897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caster Semenya\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The onslaught\", \"from\": 5812, \"to\": 5825}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 5836, \"to\": 5842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Katrina Karkazis, a professor of sexuality, women's, and gender studies at Amherst College, told us, \\\"The targeting of Khelif and so many other women athletes of color before her make it impossible to miss the optics of this controversy.\\\"\", \"from\": 5976, \"to\": 6214, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5976, \"end\": 5992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katrina_Karkazis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katrina Karkazis\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katrina_Karkazis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katrina_Karkazis\"}, {\"begin\": 6051, \"end\": 6066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amherst_College\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.2273276772426634e-30, \"text\": \"Amherst College\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amherst_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amherst_College\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a professor\", \"from\": 5994, \"to\": 6005}, {\"ngram\": \"sexuality\", \"from\": 6009, \"to\": 6018}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 6020, \"to\": 6025}, {\"ngram\": \"gender studies\", \"from\": 6033, \"to\": 6047}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 6073, \"to\": 6075}, {\"ngram\": \"The targeting\", \"from\": 6078, \"to\": 6091}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 6095, \"to\": 6101}, {\"ngram\": \"so many other women athletes\", \"from\": 6106, \"to\": 6134}, {\"ngram\": \"color\", \"from\": 6138, \"to\": 6143}, {\"ngram\": \"the optics\", \"from\": 6182, \"to\": 6192}, {\"ngram\": \"this controversy\", \"from\": 6196, \"to\": 6212}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The situation, she said, \\\"reflects the racial politics that emerged in the context of Western colonialism, where racialized ideals about women's bodies were used to construct women who do not fit the ideal as somehow outside the natural order.\\\"\", \"from\": 6215, \"to\": 6459, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6301, \"end\": 6320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colonialism\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3557036643565565e-26, \"text\": \"Western colonialism\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colonialism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colonialism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The situation\", \"from\": 6215, \"to\": 6228}, {\"ngram\": \"the racial politics\", \"from\": 6250, \"to\": 6269}, {\"ngram\": \"the context\", \"from\": 6286, \"to\": 6297}, {\"ngram\": \"racialized ideals\", \"from\": 6328, \"to\": 6345}, {\"ngram\": \"women's bodies\", \"from\": 6352, \"to\": 6366}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 6390, \"to\": 6395}, {\"ngram\": \"the ideal\", \"from\": 6411, \"to\": 6420}, {\"ngram\": \"the natural order\", \"from\": 6440, \"to\": 6457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Karkazis added, \\\"What makes these episodes dangerous is the way these terrorizing systems view the very existence of these women as the problem, rather than racism, sexism, or homophobia.\\\"\", \"from\": 6461, \"to\": 6649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Karkazis\", \"from\": 6461, \"to\": 6469}, {\"ngram\": \"these episodes\", \"from\": 6489, \"to\": 6503}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 6517, \"to\": 6524}, {\"ngram\": \"these terrorizing systems\", \"from\": 6525, \"to\": 6550}, {\"ngram\": \"the very existence\", \"from\": 6556, \"to\": 6574}, {\"ngram\": \"these women\", \"from\": 6578, \"to\": 6589}, {\"ngram\": \"the problem\", \"from\": 6593, \"to\": 6604}, {\"ngram\": \"racism\", \"from\": 6618, \"to\": 6624}, {\"ngram\": \"sexism\", \"from\": 6626, \"to\": 6632}, {\"ngram\": \"homophobia\", \"from\": 6637, \"to\": 6647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This fresh wave of attacks against women of color has also emerged amid Trump's racist, floundering presidential campaign.\", \"from\": 6651, \"to\": 6773, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6723, \"end\": 6728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.782315558833147e-17, \"text\": \"Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This fresh wave\", \"from\": 6651, \"to\": 6666}, {\"ngram\": \"attacks\", \"from\": 6670, \"to\": 6677}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 6686, \"to\": 6691}, {\"ngram\": \"color\", \"from\": 6695, \"to\": 6700}, {\"ngram\": \"presidential campaign\", \"from\": 6751, \"to\": 6772}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Desperate for an issue to divide and inflame, Trump's toadies have taken a break from going after the Olympic opening ceremony and swerved their attention onto the Algerian boxer like a cat chasing a Fox News laser pointer.\", \"from\": 6774, \"to\": 6997, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6820, \"end\": 6825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.782315558833147e-17, \"text\": \"Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 6938, \"end\": 6946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al